Add and reorder columns

add_deployment_columns.Rd

Add deployment_range, and sensor_type, sensor_serial number columns. Rename depth column to sensor_depth_at_low_tide_m.

Usage

add_deployment_columns(dat, start_date, end_date, sn_table)

Arguments

dat

placeholder

start_date

placeholder

end_date

placeholder

sn_table

A data frame with three columns: sensor_type, sensor_serial_number, depth.

Value

returns dat with additional columns
